{"tid":1235503,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【多圖】傅穎唔再化「膠樣妝」　Post偽素顏照自己平反！","createTime":"2019-06-17T07:02:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T13:01:55.000Z","uid":147370,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"940ee3cdecaf4ae878fdcaf4bf2f8d8fcb602362","tid":1235503,"uid":147370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:02:02.000Z","msg":"現年34歲的傅穎（Theresa）於五年前到內地發展後長居北京，但不時都在IG post相與香港fans互動。她最近就上載了一輯自然乾淨的「偽素顏」照片，為自己平反力證純天然！<br />\n<br />\nTheresa從2002年18歲出道以來，精緻的五官一直被質疑曾多次整容，雖然她解釋過好多次，一切都係化妝技巧同攝影角度影響，甚至拍了一條教「化膠樣妝」的短片。雖然妝前妝後差別很大，但都未能打破被質疑整容的傳聞。"},{"pid":"25b4a883904710dcf83bdafbcb17d582f548b361","tid":1235503,"uid":147370,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V4ed9vt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV4ed9vt.png&h=5f93c931&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XM64wJO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXM64wJO.png&h=0ae3f4fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QCAtdW9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQCAtdW9.png&h=23e07145&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/697WnQv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F697WnQv.png&h=0ad7bace&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2rXbWav.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2rXbWav.png&h=f01366da&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"712b31d8d5a6eb26c450d1bc75690e91bc594eb3","tid":1235503,"uid":70754,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"素了？"},{"pid":"b797647bf59b1211afe759f0f49353e78ec6f775","tid":1235503,"uid":147370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"712b31d8d5a6eb26c450d1bc75690e91bc594eb3","tid":1235503,"uid":70754,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T07:04:14.000Z","msg":"素了？"},"citedBy